_A_SELECT_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION_: ASelect is a component that allows users to make one or more choices from a predefined list of options.
_A_SELECT_GROUP_GROUPS_DESCRIPTION_: Select options in a dropdown can be customized by grouping them by one or multiple keys.
_A_SELECT_GROUP_KEY_DISABLED_DESCRIPTION: Select option values in a dropdown can be disabled based on the object key for each option.
_A_SELECT_GROUP_SEARCH_DESCRIPTION_: Select options values can be filtered based on the search query. This is useful for components with a long list of options, makeing it easier for users for find and choose the needed option.
_A_SELECT_GROUP_TRANSLATE_DATA_DESCRIPTI: Translations of labels are supported for dropdown options. Search is also supported with localized, translated options.
